high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Pick the banana from the wash basin.
Turn left and head towards the diningtable.
Place the banana on the diningtable.
Turn left and move to the shelf.
Pick another banana from the second row of the rack.
Turn back to the diningtable.
Now place that banana on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: To place the banana on the dining table.

high_descs: Walk out of the bedroom and go to the sink.
Pick up one banana from the cabinet top.
Take the banana to the diningtable.
Place the banana on top of the diningtable.
Go to the shelf and get another banana.
Take the banana and walk over to the kitchen table.
Hold on to the banana for a while.
Place the banana down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Gather the bananas and put them on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the doorway, then head towards the sink in the bathroom to your right
Pick up the banana on the right side
Turn around and walk to the room on your right, head towards the dining table
Put the banana on the dining table
Walk to the shelf on your left
Pick up the banana from the shelf
Go back to the dining table on your right
Put the banana on the dining table on the right side
anns.task_desc: Put two banana on a dining table
